author: By JANET McCONNAUGHEY Associated Press
title: Louisiana governor: stay-home order 'may well' be extended
description: NEW ORLEANS (AP) — Orders closing many Louisiana businesses and keeping people home to slow the spread of COVID-19 ‘may well’ have to be extended past April 13, Gov. John Bel Edwards said Sunday.
